.TH pif-registry-clean 1  "pif-registry-clean " 
.SH NAME
pif\-registry\-clean \- Remove registry entries whose install paths no longer exist on disk
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBpif\-registry\-clean\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Remove registry entries whose install paths no longer exist on disk
.PP
Scans every recorded installation path and removes entries whose directory or file is gone. Useful after manually deleting extensions.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
